               <p>Q. Is Mr. 
               <persName id="t18100411-138-person1121">James</persName>
             a customer of yours - A. Yes. The prisoner came on the 31st of March and brought this order which I have in my hand.</p>
               <p>"Please to let the bearer have two gross of each of the patterns. 
               <persName id="t18100411-138-person1122">
                  Francis 
                  James
               <interp inst="t18100411-138-person1122" type="surname" value="James"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18100411-138-person1122" type="given" value="Francis"></interp>
